{"id":482,"date":"2025-11-19T10:11:09","date_gmt":"2025-11-19T10:11:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.commmp.com\/index.php\/about-us\/"},"modified":"2026-03-13T11:24:54","modified_gmt":"2026-03-13T11:24:54","slug":"about-us","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.commmp.com\/","title":{"rendered":"About Us"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-23b1a4dc wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-23b1a4dc wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-23b1a4dc wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-23b1a4dc wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-23b1a4dc wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-23b1a4dc wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left\">We are more than just equipment sellers\u2014we are your knowledgeable telecommunication industry consultants.<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Our main business includes a wide range of communication equipment and materials:<br>\u2022 Optical Access Network: Full series of OLT, ONU, ONT, GPON, EPON<br>\u2022 Transmission &amp; Supporting: Full series of SFP modules, Passive WDM, pigtails, patch cords, dummy test fibers, etc.<br>\u2022 Power Equipment: Base station embedded power supplies, OLT power supplies, power rectifier modules, etc.<br>\u2022 Terminals &amp; Accessories: Engineering equipment and various communication supplies and accessories (e.g., fiber cleavers, fiber holders, etc.)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Our Advantage:<\/strong><br>Our team has years of experience in communication engineering design and has been deeply involved in the planning and design of 5G\/4G\/NB, bearer\/access networks, FTTH, and more. Although technical consulting is not our core service, this background allows us to better understand your pain points when helping you select the right products.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We fully understand the compatibility requirements of network architectures. Therefore, instead of offering complex network design services, we focus on: quickly recommending the optimal brand combinations and equipment configurations based on your needs\u2014helping you get the most site-appropriate products within a reasonable budget.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing us means partnering with a supply chain expert who has the technology, the resources, and the reliability you can count on.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\"><strong>Due to the large number of SKUs, we only display some of our products online. The prices shown are for retail only. If you are a wholesaler, distributor, engineering contractor, or network service operator, please contact us to negotiate the most favorable pricing. We have a complete range of communication products available\u2014welcome to inquire!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We are more than just equipment sellers\u2014we are your knowledgeable telecommunication industry consultants. Our main business includes a wide range [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_uag_custom_page_level_css":"","site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"default","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"disabled","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"","ast-featured-img":"","footer-sml-layout":"","ast-disable-related-posts":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"enabled","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-stick-meta":"","header-below-stick-meta":"","astra-migrate-meta-layouts":"default","ast-page-background-enabled":"default","ast-page-background-meta":{"desktop":{"background-color":"var(--ast-global-color-4)","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","background-position":"center center","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media":"","overlay-type":"","overlay-color":"","overlay-opacity":"","overlay-gradient":""},"tablet":{"bac